@startuml
actor User
participant "Daily Planning App" as System
participant Task
participant "Unavailable Hours" as UH
participant Plan
participant "Notification Service" as NS

User -> System: Select "Create Daily Plan"
System -> Task: Fetch tasks
Task --> System: Task list

System -> UH: Load unavailable hours
UH --> System: Unavailable hours

System -> System: Analyze tasks
(priorities & durations)
System -> Plan: Create daily plan
Plan --> System: Daily plan

System -> User: Display plan
User -> System: Approve plan

System -> Plan: Save plan
System -> NS: Schedule reminders
NS --> System: Reminders scheduled

System -> User: Plan created confirmation
@enduml
